    content: "A condition is a temporary game state. The definition of a condition says how it affects its recipient, and various rules define how to end a condition. This glossary defines these conditions:\nBlinded\nCharmed\nDeafened\nExhaustion\nFrightened\nGrappled\nIncapacitated\nInvisible\nParalyzed\nPetrified\nPoisoned\nProne\nRestrained\nStunned\nUnconscious\nA condition doesn't stack with itself; a recipient either has a condition or doesn't. The Exhaustion condition is an exception to that rule.",
